text: 350px Portrait of Stéphane Mallarmé is an 1876 oil on canvas portrait by Edouard Manet of his friend, the poet Stéphane Mallarmé.https://www.google.com/culturalinstitute/beta/asset/wd/dQE80gCkrM68mAhttps://www.pop.culture.gouv.fr/notice/joconde/000PE003903 It is now in the Musée d'Orsay, which was acquired from the subject himself.http://www.musee-orsay.fr/fr/collections/catalogue-des- oeuvres/notice.html?nnumid=1133 ==References== Mallarme category:1876 paintings Category:Paintings of the Musée d'Orsay Mallarme
